Sketches include "The Ronny Horror Show," "Friday Edition," "Calvin Klein Jeans takeoff," "Nat E. Dred- Rastafarian Chef," "Matzoi," and "Square Trees." Steve Forbert performs "Romeo's Tune," "Lonely Girl" and "Get Well Soon." NOTE: Reruns of this episode edit out "The Ronny Horror Show," after producers of The Rocky Horror Picture Show complained that the parody was used without their permission.
